<p style="margin: 0px; display: inline;"><span style="font-size:14px;">N&aacute;dhern&eacute; jesenn&eacute; počasie n&aacute;m prialo keď sme sa vybrali s Oľgou Best&auml;ndigovou (olympijsk&aacute; krasokorčuliarka v&nbsp;Salt Lake City 2002) na tr&eacute;ning pri bratislavskom Draždiaku. Priniesli sme na testovanie na&scaron;u nov&uacute;&nbsp;<strong><a href="damska-kolekcia-fitness"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;"><span aria-label="hashtag" class="_58cl">‪</span></span></a><span class="_58cm"><a href="damska-kolekcia-fitness" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">FITNESS</span></a><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">‬</span></span></strong>&nbsp;kolekciu, v ktorej Oľga odcvičila&nbsp;cel&yacute; tr&eacute;ning. Na strečing mala Oľga oblečen&uacute; &scaron;portov&uacute; <a href="http://www.carpedmfashion.com/damske-mikiny">mikinu s kapucňou</a> <strong><a href="damske-oblecenie/kolekcia-fitness/damska-sportova-mikina-fay-in-fit" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">FAY IN FIT</span></a></strong> a&nbsp;elastick&eacute; nohavice <strong><a href="damske-oblecenie/kolekcia-fitness/damske-elasticke-nohavice-long-fit" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">LONG FIT</span></a></strong>, ktor&eacute; vyr&aacute;bame&nbsp;v troch farb&aacute;ch. Na behanie na hrej&uacute;com&nbsp;slnku&nbsp;si Oľga nechala hore už len&nbsp;&scaron;portov&uacute; podprsenku <strong><a href="damske-oblecenie/kolekcia-fitness/damska-sportova-podprsenka-h-fit" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">H FIT</span></a></strong>, ktor&aacute; v&yacute;borne drž&iacute; a je veľmi pohodln&aacute;. Kr&aacute;tky hodinov&yacute; tr&eacute;ning ukončila Oľga cvičen&iacute;m hornej časti tela na hrazde&nbsp;v kr&aacute;tkych elastick&yacute;ch nohaviciach <strong><a href="damske-oblecenie/kolekcia-fitness/damske-elasticke-sortky-short-fit" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">SHORT FIT</span></a></strong>&nbsp;so &scaron;portovou podprsenkou <strong><a href="damske-oblecenie/kolekcia-fitness/damska-sportova-podprsenka-x-fit" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">X FIT</span></a></strong>. Po tr&eacute;ningu sa Oľga prezliekla do pohodlnej a skvele vyzeraj&uacute;cej <a href="http://www.carpedmfashion.com/damske-teplaky">tepl&aacute;kovej s&uacute;pravy</a> zloženej zo &scaron;portov&yacute;ch tepl&aacute;kov <strong><a href="damske-oblecenie/kolekcia-fitness/damske-elasticke-teplaky-squared-fit" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">SQUARED FIT</span></a>&nbsp;</strong>a mikiny s dlh&yacute;m golierom na zips <strong><a href="damske-oblecenie/kolekcia-fitness/damska-sportova-mikina-true-fit" target="_blank"><span style="color:#ADD8E6;">TRUE FIT</span></a></strong>, ktor&aacute; ju ochr&aacute;ni pred chladn&yacute;m jesenn&yacute;m vetrom a v ktorej sa bude c&iacute;tiť pohodlne a &scaron;t&yacute;lovo, keď sa stretne po tr&eacute;ningu&nbsp;s priateľmi v kaviarni.</span></p>
